      "text": [
        " قَالَ رَسُولُ اللَّهِ ص إِنَّ أَعَقَّ النَّاسِ عَلَی اللَّهِ تَعَالَی مَنْ قَتَلَ غَیْرَ قَاتِلِهِ وَ مَنْ ضَرَبَ مَنْ لَمْ یَضْرِبْهُ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.sayed-athar-husain-rizvi-&-sayed-maqsood-athar": [
          "7.  Imam  Ja’far  Sadiq  (a.s.)  said,  “A  person most unjust  in Allah’s eyes is one who kills a person who hasn’t murdered him or hurt one who did not hurt him.”"
        ]
